OL,5, An anonymous hotline will be set up for
OL,6, people to report Met Police officers   
OL,7, and staff for corruption, abuse and    
OL,8, other breaches of trust or power.      
OL,10,FRecent scandals to hit the force       
OL,11,Finclude strip-searching children, the  
OL,12,Fmurder of Sarah Everard, and the       
OL,13,Fsharing of pictures of Bibaa Henry and 
OL,14,FNicole Smallman after they were killed.
OL,16,FOfficers have been convicted of a      
OL,17,Fstring of offences including sex       
OL,18,Fcrimes, theft and assault.             
OL,20,FThe line will be run by Crimestoppers. 
